# Default-deny everything in parsed_data/ (PDF re-extraction outputs are
# heavy and regenerable). Specific curated deliverables are re-included
# below — these are SSOT inputs to downstream WIs and must travel with
# the repo.
/parsed_data/*
# FR-156 Phase 5 WI-A1 deliverable — curated bare→versed map for the
# 6 firstVespers psalms. Tracked because WI-A2 rewrite + WI-C catalog
# augmentation consume it as SSOT. Regenerable via
#   `node scripts/extract-first-vespers-versed-map.js`
# (anchored against parsed_data/full_pdf.txt, which stays untracked).
!/parsed_data/first-vespers-versed-map.json
/output_sample.txt
/parsed_raw.txt
/psalter_full_text.txt
# PDF plain-text dump — regenerated by `pdftotext -layout public/psalter.pdf
